articles.title: Tiger Woods’ son Charlie chuckles while watching his dad suffer heavy defeat in TGL debut - Yahoo Sports
articles.description: Tiger Woods’ debut in the TGL, a new high-tech indoor golf league, ended in disappointment on Tuesday, as his Jupiter Links Golf Club team was thrashed 12-1 by Los Angeles Golf Club.
